<br>
All trials seem to have the standard 4 waves.<br>
<br>
Try hanging next... kill spirits of suffocation quickly even if it means switching off a mob when one pops.  If you let the spirits of suffocation live you'll notice the 3 prisoners fall down one by one.  They'll stand up again when spirit dies.  My guess is when all 3 are down you lose. The other 2 types aren't too big of a deal.  The lizards have a fun proc. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  (beat this 1st time)<br>
<br>
Lashing isn't too hard.  Kill mobs until lasher spawns then send someone down the 3 halls to kill the sprites to make lasher despawn.  1 of the 3 sprites will make the lasher despawn.  Lasher is a naked DE with a whip.  You can't target him to taunt or attack.  AEtaunt may work, but it's easier to just to train him on a tank. Kill waves until the boss spawns.  (beat this 2nd round, lasher ate cleric first time)<br>
<br>
Stoning is not too bad.  Kill mobs to make the archers stop.  Kill fast or the archers will kill the prisoners.  Mobs come from doors to left and right of the prisoners.  Once mobs are out the rooms are a good place for your cleric/casters to duck out so they don't get hit by stones.  Get them out before the next wave tho!  (beat this one 1st time)<br>
<br>
Torture is a marathon.  The waves seemed to overlap.  I guess we were killing too slow, but was same group as the other trials we did.   Robes can be mez'd.  Was nonstop killing the entire time and our casters were all oom at the end. (beat this one 1st time)<br>
<br>
Flame we lost 3 times in a row.   4 mobs spawn and start moving toward the center.  If they reach the center they stand there for about 30seconds and then poof you lose.  I saw 2 types of mobs.  Elementals and another type (lizard model i think).    Elementals can be mez'd.   Waves come fast so you need HIGH dps.   Probably the hardest trial.<br>
<br>
<br>
Hope that helps. <p>Gaptooth the Champion<br>
